Altium Designer v16.0.5 Build 271
---------------------------------------------------
___________________________________________________
1. Unistall old version Altium Designer.
2. Run AltiumDesigner16Setup.exe
3. Select and install the required modules
4. Not run Altium Designer
5. Copy  msimg32.dll from folder Medicine in folder Altium Designer and replace
6. Run Altium Designer and select any license from folder Licenses/
7. Enjoy
